Title: Twin Peaks
Actors: Kyle MacLachlan, Michael Ontkean, Sheryl Lee, Catherine E. Coulson, Heather Graham, Kenneth Welsh, Frank Silva, Russ Tamblyn, Wendy Robie, Eric DaRe, Harry Goaz, Michael Horse, Michael J. Anderson, Chris Mulkey, Piper Laurie, Warren Frost, Kimmy Robertson, Ray Wise, Joan Chen, Jack Nance, Everett McGill, James Marshall
Plot: The body of a young girl (Laura Palmer) is washed up on a beach near the small Washington state town of Twin Peaks. FBI Special Agent Dale Cooper is called in to investigate her strange demise only to uncover a web of mystery that ultimately leads him deep into the heart of the surrounding woodland and his very own soul.
